short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds min/max price filters to the Fooda browse items page

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Finally you can filter by price! If you want to filter by min/max price instead of using just 3 presets: "Below $7, $7-$9, Above $9", then this is an extension for you.
